<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Reminder - PropertyOS</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f59e0b;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #f59e0b;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .alert-box {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .alert-box h3 {
      color: #92400e;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .info-value {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .amount {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ef4444;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #4338ca;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>PropertyOS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Payment Reminder</h2>
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>This is a friendly reminder that your rent payment is <span class="highlight">due soon</span>.</p>

      <div class="alert-box">
        <h3>⚠️ Payment Due Date</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0;">Your payment of <strong>${{paymentAmount}}</strong> is due on <strong>{{dueDate}}</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Payment Amount</span>
          <span class="info-value amount">${{paymentAmount}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Due Date</span>
          <span class="info-value highlight">{{dueDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Property</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{propertyAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Unit</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{unitNumber}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if gracePeriodDays}}
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Grace Period</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{gracePeriodDays}} days</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if lateFeeAmount}}
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Late Fee After Grace Period</span>
          <span class="info-value" style="color: #dc2626;">${{lateFeeAmount}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      {{#if paymentUrl}}
      <a href="{{paymentUrl}}" class="button">Make Payment Now</a>
      {{/if}}

      <p>Please ensure your payment is made on time to avoid any late fees. If you've already made this payment, please disregard this notice.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance with your payment, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} PropertyOS. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>